;; ============================================================================
;; SHARED EVAL FIXTURE — a fictional test persona's ledger.
;;
;; One seed that all three eval suites read against:
;;   • Editor   — draft onto the held cards below (held-account matching, cashback
;;                pattern, points accrual, balances, edits).
;;   • Statement— the OPEN ACCOUNTS a real statement gets matched against (held
;;                cards across issuers + their reward pools).
;;   • Concierge— holdings-aware Q&A ("best card I have for X", "which of my cards
;;                reach Avios"), points balances, and spend history.
;;
;; PRIVACY: the card PRODUCTS are real public cards — they MUST be, so the agents
;; resolve them in the KG (card_guide / EARNS_INTO / transfer paths). Everything
;; else — that this persona holds them, every balance, merchant, amount and date —
;; is INVENTED. No real person's data appears here. Keep it that way: synthetic,
;; round, obviously-fictional (see CLAUDE.md).
;;
;; "Today" for the suites is 2026; quarters below are Q1 (Jan–Mar) and Q2 (Apr–Jun)
;; so period questions ("spend last quarter") have something to land on.
;; ============================================================================

;; ---- Reward-pool opening balances (for "my points balances across programmes")
;; The seed applies transactions only (pad/balance directives are ignored on
;; ingest), so opening balances are set as plain Equity:Void plug transactions.
2026-01-01 * "Opening balance" "HDFC reward points"
  Assets:Rewards:HDFC                           120000 HDFC-RP-INFINIA
  Equity:Void                                  -120000 HDFC-RP-INFINIA

2026-01-01 * "Opening balance" "Axis EDGE Miles"
  Assets:Rewards:Axis                            45000 AXIS-EM-ATLAS
  Equity:Void                                   -45000 AXIS-EM-ATLAS

2026-01-01 * "Opening balance" "Avios"
  Assets:Rewards:Avios                           30000 AVIOS
  Equity:Void                                   -30000 AVIOS

2026-01-01 * "Opening balance" "Amex Membership Rewards"
  Assets:Rewards:Amex                            80000 MR
  Equity:Void                                   -80000 MR

2026-01-01 * "Opening balance" "Marriott Bonvoy"
  Assets:Rewards:MarriottBonvoy                  95000 MARRIOTTBONVOY
  Equity:Void                                   -95000 MARRIOTTBONVOY

2026-01-01 * "Opening balance" "SBI reward points"
  Assets:Rewards:SBI                             15000 SBI-RP
  Equity:Void                                   -15000 SBI-RP

;; ---- HDFC Infinia (points, transfers via SmartBuy) ----
;; Dining spend with the 5 RP / ₹150 accrual to :Pending.
2026-02-09 * "Cafe Aroma" "Dining out"
  Expenses:Food:Restaurants                    1500.00 INR
  Liabilities:CreditCards:HDFC:Infinia        -1500.00 INR
  Assets:Rewards:HDFC:Pending                       50 HDFC-RP-INFINIA
  Equity:Void                                      -50 HDFC-RP-INFINIA

2026-03-18 * "MetroMobiles" "New phone"
  Expenses:Shopping:Electronics               60000.00 INR
  Liabilities:CreditCards:HDFC:Infinia       -60000.00 INR
  Assets:Rewards:HDFC:Pending                     2000 HDFC-RP-INFINIA
  Equity:Void                                    -2000 HDFC-RP-INFINIA

;; Points posted (Pending -> settled), the documented credit pattern.
2026-04-03 * "HDFC Rewards" "Feb–Mar points posted"
  Assets:Rewards:HDFC                             2050 HDFC-RP-INFINIA
  Assets:Rewards:HDFC:Pending                    -2050 HDFC-RP-INFINIA

