  Expenses:Travel:Flights                      28000.00 INR
  Liabilities:CreditCards:Axis:Atlas          -28000.00 INR
  Assets:Rewards:Axis:Pending                      560 AXIS-EM-ATLAS
  Equity:Void                                     -560 AXIS-EM-ATLAS

