  Expenses:Travel:Hotels                       18000.00 INR
  Liabilities:CreditCards:Axis:Atlas          -18000.00 INR
  Assets:Rewards:Axis:Pending                      360 AXIS-EM-ATLAS
  Equity:Void                                     -360 AXIS-EM-ATLAS

