;; ---- A REDEMPTION (points -> award), for "which of these are redemptions" ----
;; 25,000 Avios redeemed for a flight worth ₹21,000 (cpp carried as @@ on the leg).
2026-06-04 * "SkyHigh Airlines" "Award flight — points redemption"
  Expenses:Travel:Flights                     21000.00 INR
  Assets:Rewards:Avios                          -25000 AVIOS @@ 21000.00 INR

